mefene, Nicotine, Codeine, Morphine, Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, Meperidine, More', 'Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Tepotinib, Avapritinib, Selumetinib, Cobimetinib, Capmatinib, Ibrutinib, Afatinib, Tivozanib, Zanubrutinib, More', 1767369485);
